ActCanadian Wheat Board Act
SubjectCanada Amber Durum ** August 2010 - July 2011 INITIAL PAYMENTS **
PrecisOrder a) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2010-946 of July 19, 2010; and b) approving the increase by the Canadian Wheat Board of the initial payments for grades other than the base grade of AMBER DURUM WHEAT for the pool period commencing on August 1, 2010 and ending on July 31, 2011.
